tts.  We had 3 clerics or so, but not enough damage dealers and rampge took a lot of us out.<br>
<br>
Also, the elders and cheftians got buffed up a lot as well.  Pretty sure I remember them being unslowable now.  They are however and EXCELLENT source of etheral parchments.  They dropped one nearly every time.  No spec parchments or runes though like before the nerf bat swung. <p>-Timmoy da fattie Warlord 
